<A>__{running... rocky's crowd of trailing boys has tripled. dashing through the streets, he resembles the pied piper.}
<L>__{exterior art museum stairs day}
<A>__{it is twilight and rocky is alone at the very bottom of a huge flight of steps that seem to stretch into the heavens... rocky takes a deep breath and sprints up the never ending stairs... halfway up, his body shows the strain. nearing the top, rocky pumps with all his strength and arrives at the very top... he looks down the steep stairs and swells with pride... he is ready.}
